Repository: https://github.com/CheeseMochi/lightshowpi-neo

LightShowPi Neo is a significant modernization and fork of the original
LightShowPi project. While based on the original codebase, Neo includes
substantial refactoring, new features, and divergent design decisions.

See FORK.md for detailed information about the relationship between
LightShowPi Neo and the original LightShowPi project.

